column120: We’re on an A/B schedule. I serve the entire 5th grade this year. I don’t care which days you come, but I’d need it to be on 2 consecutive days. Example: (Monday/Tuesday) or (Tuesday/Wednesday)

column120: My first science class is an inclusion class so we have about 6 kids with IEPs involving learning accommodations. The class as a whole requires extra patience to work best and the 6 with IEPs usually thrive with fill in notes. I do have a para professional who helps out in that class too. My second science class is our honors group so they will work faster through whatever activities planned and tend to like to ask questions about why something occurs. My last science class is somewhere in between with lots of energy.
